        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Introducing B. F. Foster.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>Dear ser.</p>

<p>My friend <persName>Col. Benjamin F Fauster</persName> will hand you this;</p>

<p>The <persName>Col</persName>. is the <persName>agent for the Texas Association Company</persName> and will
reside in that <placeName>Country</placeName>.</p>

<p>You will find him an intelligent Gentlemanly <persName>man</persName>, and one in
whom you will be pleased on an acquaintance&#8212;any services you can
render him whilst in your <placeName>Country </placeName>will be acknowledged etc.&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>Robt Desha</persName></p>

<p>[Addressed:] <persName>Col. Stephen F Austin</persName> <placeName>Austins Grant Texas Pr.
</placeName><persName>Col. Fauster</persName></p>



        </div1>
